message:

title: 820-2914 Fan on high Speed & slow.
message:
I don't see Palm Proximity in the photo.
But if is the case, then try known good trackpad board and flex.
Such sensor is embedded in the trackpad circuitry.
Also check continuity between U5550 and corresponding sensors, Q5501/03.

title: 820-2914 Fan on high Speed & slow.
message: Any device connected on the same SMBus can generate the same problem.

title: 820-2914 Fan on high Speed & slow.
message: SOLVED. As GPU Proximity/GPU Die/Left Heat Pipe/Right Fin Stack controlled by U5550, I replaced U5550 . Bingo. ...Thank you very much for your support. Until I trouble you again take care.:)
